  "text": "For the control towards 1 and in the monostable case (H1), the Lyapunov functional introduced in Remark 1 works in arbitrary dimension [CITATION_1] . For the control towards θ in the bistable case (H2) with the static strategy of putting θ on the whole of ∂Ω, there is also a threshold as can be proved thanks to the above result.",
